  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-Op Gameplay Experience</h2>Explore, drill, and produce oil on your own or team up with up to five friends. Work together for faster progress and make strategic decisions to run a successful operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oil Exploration and Extraction</h2>Lease land from the municipality to search for oil. Extract crude oil and transport it to your storage facilities using barrels or tanker trucks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Item Production and Market Sales</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Process crude oil into petroleum products using industrial machinery, then set your own prices and sell them in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fuel Production and Sales</h2>Refine crude oil into a variety of fuels such as diesel and gasoline. Negotiate with gas stations to sell your products and maximize your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Valuable Discoveries</h2>During excavations, you’ll uncover not only oil but also precious gems, fossils, and minerals. Add them to your collection and earn extra revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipment Upgrades</h2>Enhance everything from your detectors and vehicles to your oil pumps. Expand your brand and grow your factory to increase efficiency and output.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ultimate Goal: Become the City’s Leading Oil Supplier</h2>As you earn more money, unlock new regions, acquire larger equipment, and aim to become the sole provider of oil that powers the entire city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready for a strategic, cooperative, and exploratory adventure!</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Co-Op Gameplay Experience</h2>Explore, drill, and produce oil on your own or team up with up to five friends. Work together for faster progress and make strategic decisions to run a successful operation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Oil Exploration and Extraction</h2>Lease land from the municipality to search for oil. Extract crude oil and transport it to your storage facilities using barrels or tanker trucks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/97f2775e6269c4316893c8bda1006239.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Item Production and Market Sales</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Process crude oil into petroleum products using industrial machinery, then set your own prices and sell them in your shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/70a55b4ba4b8c7f10cdb00af61696f71.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fuel Production and Sales</h2>Refine crude oil into a variety of fuels such as diesel and gasoline. Negotiate with gas stations to sell your products and maximize your profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Valuable Discoveries</h2>During excavations, you’ll uncover not only oil but also precious gems, fossils, and minerals. Add them to your collection and earn extra revenue.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/fd4ffffbcd38c990e7d7256db8fa2831.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Equipment Upgrades</h2>Enhance everything from your detectors and vehicles to your oil pumps. Expand your brand and grow your factory to increase efficiency and output.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ultimate Goal: Become the City’s Leading Oil Supplier</h2>As you earn more money, unlock new regions, acquire larger equipment, and aim to become the sole provider of oil that powers the entire city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.poster.avif?t=1770051125\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.webm?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3441460/extras/faa97fddbd12e6387424759b6964c671.mp4?t=1770051125\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready for a strategic, cooperative, and exploratory adventure!</strong></p>",
